nodes.text: Thats what I thought..... no defense for your perverse behavior.

And you offer none for your's. Heteros engage is risky business as well. Therefore on the same grounds we ban straight marriage.  It's not just STD's, it's all sorts of physical issues as well. Cancers, hepatitus, bacterial infections, that result from anal and vagina sex. Add one word and BAM, it works aganist you.

Actually, it's not a good point. I usually question the maturity of people who judge other people by where they were born and raised. There are good things about every state. Louisianna is just as good as any other state. So are most of the people who live there. There are crooks in every state, also.

Because there are good things about every state means....what exactly? Of course there is good in bad in most everything, which has nothing to do with what I said. Yes, great food, crawfish as a staple, great fishing, bayous, New Orleans, Mardi Gras....long beads......sure, some great things. With regards to achievement or vision? I'm not seeing it. Legal gambling? That was another recent 'achievement'. What about wanting to secede from the Union? Yes, Louisiana is the consistent trend-setter for the civilized world. Oh wait, it isn't. -Mach
